---
// src/components/Community.astro
---
<section class="section-dark pt-8 pb-20 sm:pb-28">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-5 sm:px-8 lg:px-12">
 
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-20">
      <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-3 mb-5">
        <span class="w-8 h-px bg-amber-400/40"></span>
        <span class="font-body text-amber-500 text-xs tracking-[0.25em] uppercase">Giving Back</span>
        <span class="w-8 h-px bg-amber-400/40"></span>
      </div>
      <span class="gold-line mx-auto"></span>
      <h1 class="section-heading text-4xl sm:text-5xl text-white mb-6">
        Siyakhathalela.<br/>
        <span class="text-amber-400">We Care.</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="font-body text-gray-400 text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed">
        eKoneni isn't just where Mdantsane grooves — it's where Mdantsane looks after its own.
        The same energy poured into every Friday night gets poured into the streets,
        the families, and the children of this community.
      </p>
    </div>
 
    <!-- Initiative 1 — Feeding Scheme -->
    <div class="community-card rounded-2xl overflow-hidden mb-8">
      <div class="h-1.5 bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-400 to-amber-600"></div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2">
 
        <div class="p-8 sm:p-12 flex flex-col justify-center">
          <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-amber-400/10 border border-amber-400/20 font-body text-amber-400 text-xs tracking-widest uppercase mb-5">
            Feeding Scheme · 2024
          </span>
          <h2 class="section-heading text-3xl sm:text-4xl text-white mb-5">
            No Child Goes <span class="text-amber-400">Hungry.</span>
          </h2>
          <p class="font-body text-gray-400 text-base leading-relaxed mb-4">
            For two weeks, eKoneni Lounge ran a community feeding scheme for children in Mdantsane —
            making sure every child in the neighbourhood had a proper meal each day.
            No fanfare. No conditions. Just food on the table.
          </p>
          <p class="font-body text-gray-400 text-base leading-relaxed">
            This is the eKoneni way. A business that takes from a community without giving back is no
            business at all. <span class="text-amber-200/80">Sibanakekelene</span> — we look after each other.
          </p>
        </div>
 
        <!-- Photo placeholder — swap src when real photo is available -->
        <div class="min-h-[280px] lg:min-h-0 bg-amber-400/5 flex items-center justify-center border-t lg:border-t-0 lg:border-l border-amber-400/10">
          <div class="text-center p-8">
            <svg class="w-12 h-12 text-amber-400/30 mx-auto mb-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.25 15.75l5.159-5.159a2.25 2.25 0 013.182 0l5.159 5.159m-1.5-1.5l1.409-1.409a2.25 2.25 0 013.182 0l2.909 2.909M3.75 21h16.5M13.5 12h.008v.008H13.5V12z"/>
            </svg>
            <p class="font-body text-amber-400/40 text-sm">Photo coming soon</p>
            <p class="font-body text-amber-400/25 text-xs mt-1">Replace with real image from Facebook</p>
          </div>
        </div>
 
      </div>
    </div>
 
    <!-- Initiative 2 — House Rebuild -->
    <div class="community-card rounded-2xl overflow-hidden mb-20">
      <div class="h-1.5 bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-600 to-amber-400"></div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2">
 
        <!-- Photo placeholder — swap src when real photo is available -->
        <div class="order-2 lg:order-1 min-h-[280px] lg:min-h-0 bg-amber-400/5 flex items-center justify-center border-t lg:border-t-0 lg:border-r border-amber-400/10">
          <div class="text-center p-8">
            <svg class="w-12 h-12 text-amber-400/30 mx-auto mb-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.25 15.75l5.159-5.159a2.25 2.25 0 013.182 0l5.159 5.159m-1.5-1.5l1.409-1.409a2.25 2.25 0 013.182 0l2.909 2.909M3.75 21h16.5M13.5 12h.008v.008H13.5V12z"/>
            </svg>
            <p class="font-body text-amber-400/40 text-sm">Photo coming soon</p>
            <p class="font-body text-amber-400/25 text-xs mt-1">Replace with real image from media coverage</p>
          </div>
        </div>
 
        <div class="order-1 lg:order-2 p-8 sm:p-12 flex flex-col justify-center">
          <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-amber-400/10 border border-amber-400/20 font-body text-amber-400 text-xs tracking-widest uppercase mb-5">
            House Rebuild · 2025
          </span>
          <h2 class="section-heading text-3xl sm:text-4xl text-white mb-5">
            From Ashes, <span class="text-amber-400">A Home.</span>
          </h2>
          <p class="font-body text-gray-400 text-base leading-relaxed mb-4">
            When a family in Mdantsane lost everything in a house fire — their belongings, their shelter,
            their sense of safety — eKoneni stepped in without hesitation. The team took on roofing,
            painting, and structural repairs, giving a mother and her children a home to return to.
          </p>
          <p class="font-body text-gray-400 text-base leading-relaxed">
            The work continues. Electrical fitting is next. Because for eKoneni, the job isn't done
            until that family is truly home.
            <span class="text-amber-200/80">Masihlangane</span> — let us come together.
          </p>
        </div>
 
      </div>
    </div>
 
    <!-- Quote strip -->
    <div class="text-center max-w-xl mx-auto">
      <p class="font-display text-2xl sm:text-3xl text-amber-400/80 italic leading-relaxed mb-6">
        "The same Mdantsane that fills our dancefloor is the Mdantsane we go home to. We don't forget that."
      </p>
      <p class="font-body text-gray-500 text-sm mb-10">— eKoneni Lounge</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn-gold px-8 py-3.5 rounded-full font-body text-sm inline-block">
        Get In Touch
      </a>
    </div>
 
  </div>
</section>
